{"tid":1027913,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[廢老] 前晚搭車撚到個廢老激死","createTime":"2019-02-19T06:23:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-19T15:08:53.000Z","uid":202428,"like":37,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"9320ea29b86407109e1e8ccdf6b1094e4983d004","tid":1027913,"uid":202428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T06:23:11.000Z","msg":"小弟紅磡上車搭西鐵，坐咗喺關愛座，個廢老就喺尖東上車<br />\n<br />\n坐喺度督督下手機嗰陣，我無意間望上去，就見到嗰位廢老睥實我<br />\n<br />\n一開始我仲淆淆哋，唔係幾敢望，但係一諗到我哋呢班後生被人撚咗咁耐，就應該係時候撚返佢一鑊<br />\n<br />\n首先我諗到要做嘅係睥番實佢，睥睥下佢都有啲驚咗我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我覺得都係未夠，要再撚勁啲<br />\n<br />\n我企咗起身，伸個最大嘅懶腰，見住佢想行過去坐嗰陣我就一嘢坐番落去，佢個樣嬲到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好治癒<br />\n<br />\n最後想講，如果有人有需要想坐，佢出句聲問，我一定讓，但唔會係你有求於我嘅時候睥住我黑晒面咁樣，好似我讓你係應份咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be1b154391477cf38b42003648cbf0e02491c971","tid":1027913,"uid":212704,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T07:23:29.000Z","msg":"做得好 啲廢老成日持老賣老<br />\n覺得人地老鳳讓比佢地坐咁"},{"pid":"454a7e66940535aea5b815cc6ced4f7e5ecef0d5","tid":1027913,"uid":202428,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T08:28:53.000Z","msg":"推呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54063e56ed6bcb53ab17e73aa2cb2b4c45de71b7","tid":1027913,"uid":202428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T08:38:36.000Z","msg":"推呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94c0203f0d7396e1876c8ba164fe1fab2de5fcf3","tid":1027913,"uid":202428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"reply